---
import { site, waLink } from "../content/site";
import { withBase } from "../content/url";
---

<section
  id="programari"
  class="section bg-[var(--color-surface-container-low)]"
>
  <div class="container-page grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Programează-te</h2>
      <span class="gold-divider"></span>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed"
      >
        Scrie-mi pe WhatsApp sau sună-mă, spune-mi ce serviciu te interesează și
        îți confirm programarea în cel mai scurt timp.
      </p>

      <div
        class="mt-6 rounded-[1rem] bg-[var(--color-surface-container-lowest)] border border-[var(--color-outline-variant)] px-5 py-4"
      >
        <p class="label-md uppercase text-[var(--color-secondary)]">
          Bun de știut
        </p>
        <ul
          class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed"
        >
          <li>
            Programarea devine fermă după mesajul meu de confirmare pe WhatsApp.
          </li>
          <li>
            Te rog anunță-mă cu minimum <strong>24 de ore</strong> înainte dacă
            vrei să anulezi sau să reprogramezi.
          </li>
          <li>
            Detalii complete în <a
              href={withBase("/termeni/")}
              class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-[var(--color-on-surface)]"
              >Termeni și condiții</a
            >.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal md:pt-8">
      <!-- Primary action: WhatsApp. The page's single success metric, so it
           gets the strongest affordance — solid green fill, white text, the
           recognizable WhatsApp glyph, and a "fastest reply" reassurance. -->
      <a
        href={waLink()}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="btn-whatsapp group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-[1.25rem] px-6 py-5 no-underline"
      >
        <span
          class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/15 flex items-center justify-center"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
            <path d="M3 21l1.65-3.8A8.5 8.5 0 1 1 7.8 19.35L3 21z"/>
            <path d="M8.5 8.5c0 4 3 7 7 7l1.5-2-2.5-1-1 1c-1 0-3-2-3-3l1-1-1-2.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="flex-1">
          <span class="block text-base font-bold leading-tight">Scrie-mi pe WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="block mt-0.5 text-sm text-white">Răspund cel mai repede aici · {site.phone}</span>
        </span>
        <svg
          class="flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-1"
          width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Fallback: phone. Deliberately quieter so it reads as the alternative,
           not a peer of the WhatsApp CTA. -->
      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">sau, dacă preferi</p>
      <a
        href={`tel:+${site.phoneE164}`}
        class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 rounded-[1rem] border border-[var(--color-outline-variant)] px-5 py-3.5 text-[var(--color-on-surface)] no-underline hover:border-[var(--color-blush-deep)] hover:text-[var(--color-blush-deep)] transition-colors duration-200 ease-out"
      >
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.12 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.36a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="font-semibold">Sună-mă · {site.phone}</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
